    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty car, and I think you\u2019re going to love it. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me. It drives like a dream and is just waiting for its next big adventure! Whether you're heading to work or planning a road trip, this ride is ready to go. It's a great find for anyone looking for a dependable, well-cared-for vehicle. Feel free to reach out if you want to come take it for a spin!",
