    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "This 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera (996.2) features the high-revving 3.6L M96/03 flat-six engine, utilizing VarioCam Plus for an optimized torque curve across the rev range. The 6-speed manual G96 transaxle offers precise throws and mechanical feedback. Provenance is supported by a documented IMS bearing ceramic retrofit and a recent cooling system overhaul including a low-temp thermostat. The chassis retains its communicative nature with MacPherson struts up front and a multi-link rear setup that remains tight. While the exterior shows minor stone chipping, the underpinnings are dry, and the four-piston monobloc Brembo calipers provide firm, fade-resistant stopping power. A purist-spec driver\u2019s car with the mechanical vitals fully addressed.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
