    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This vehicle strikes the perfect balance between daily utility and refined performance. The exterior boasts a deep, lustrous finish with only minor road-wear consistent with its age, while the alloy wheels are wrapped in high-tread tires for a confident grip. Inside, the cabin has been meticulously maintained; the leather upholstery is supple and free of tears, and all electronic features\u2014from the premium sound system to the dual-zone climate control\u2014function flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is turn-key ready. It features a documented service history, a smooth-shifting transmission, and a responsive engine that has been recently serviced with fresh fluids and filters. It is a smoke-free, pet-free vehicle that has been garage-kept, ensuring it remains a reliable and stylish choice for its next owner.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
