    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my reliable ride, and honestly, she's been a total gem. The car is in really solid shape and has been well-loved\u2014super clean interior and it still drives like a dream! It\u2019s perfect for someone looking for a dependable daily driver that still looks great on the road. I've taken good care of the maintenance, so it's ready for its next adventure. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
