    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This 987.1-generation Cayman S is powered by the 3.4L M97 flat-six, featuring an integrated dry-sump system and VarioCam Plus for optimized valve timing. The 6-speed manual transaxle offers short, precise throws, channeling power through a chassis renowned for its low polar moment of inertia. Recent service includes a preventive water pump swap and a professional borescope inspection of the cylinders to ensure no scoring. The suspension maintains its factory-spec geometry, providing communicative feedback through the hydraulic steering rack. While the finish shows light patina from road use, the mechanical vitals are strong, offering a visceral, analog driving experience.",
